        GOOD_DAY_TO_YOU_AND_WELCOME_TO_MHAURA                                = 7856,  -- Good day to you, and welcome to Mhaura. My name is Marilionne, and I'd be happy to offer you any guidance you may need.
        GOOD_DAY_TO_YOU_AND_WELCOME_TO_SELBINA                               = 7857,  -- Good day to you, and welcome to Selbina. My name is Esteban, and I'd be happy to offer you any guidance you may need.
        IT_S_NOT_OFTEN_WE_GET_VISITORS_TO                                    = 7858,  -- It's not often we get visitors to Tavnazia. My name is Ombelotte, and I'd be...happy to offer you any guidance you may need.
        INQUIRE_ABOUT_WHAT_I_WANT_TO_FIND_SOME                               = 7859,  -- Inquire about what? I want to find some quests! I want a map of [Mhaura/Selbina]! I have other questions. Nothing for now.
        INQUIRE_ABOUT_WHAT_I_WANT_TO_FIND_SOME_2                             = 7860,  -- Inquire about what? I want to find some quests! I want a map of Tavnazia! I have other questions. Nothing for now.
        IF_YOU_BRING_ME_A_MAP_OF_THE                                         = 7861,  -- If you bring me a map of the [Windurst/San d'Oria] area, I can place a couple markers on it for you. Surely that's better than flittering around aimlessly, no?
        LUDWIG_SHOULD_BE_ABLE_TO_SELL_YOU_ONE                                = 7862,  -- Ludwig should be able to sell you one. He's south along the coast, and you'll find him on the left side of the grand plaza.
        COME_BACK_WITH_A_MAP_OF_THE_AREA                                     = 7863,  -- Come back with a map of the [San d'Oria/Windurst] area, and I'll place a couple markers to guide you on your path.
        YOU_CAN_PROCURE_ONE_FROM_LOMBARIA_ALTANA_HELP                        = 7864,  -- You can procure one from Lombaria. Altana help you if you can't find her--she's right by the door of that building in front of me!
        BRING_ME_A_MAP_OF_TAVNAZIA_AND_I                                     = 7865,  -- Bring me a map of Tavnazia, and I can mark some places that'll help set you on the right path.
        YOU_KNOW_WHO_CAN_HELP_YOU_PROCURE_A                                  = 7866,  -- You know who can help you procure a map? Elysia--provided you help her out. Let me show you where she is.
        THERE_RE_MANY_PEOPLE_BOTH_INSIDE_AND_OUTSIDE                         = 7867,  -- There're many people both inside and outside of [Mhaura/Selbina] who need an adventurer's help with some problem or other. In fact, I've got a handy list of such individuals. Want me to help you find someone?
        TAVNAZIA_MAY_LOOK_SAFE_BUT_THERE_ARE_ALWAYS                          = 7868,  -- Tavnazia may look safe, but there are always people who need an adventurer's aid. Would you like me to find some such people?
        INQUIRE_ABOUT_WHICH_LOCALE_NONE_INDIVIDUAL_INDIVIDUAL_OTHER          = 7869,  -- Inquire about which locale? None. [Mhaura/Selbina]: # individual[/s]. [Selbina/Mhaura]: # individual[/s]. Other: # individual[/s].
